{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "家康 第3话 将军世家的觉悟",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "抱歉突然进来，\\n我有件事\\n想问问尤蒂尔殿下。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "没关系。\\n你想问什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "我想知道\\n阿尔贝里亚王族的“龙化”是什么。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "虽然那和“魂契”有着相似的力量，\\n但我想一定也有不同点。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "原来是这件事啊，我明白了。\\n你尽管问吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "原来如此……\\n阿尔贝里亚王族的龙化\\n就是人与龙互相信赖的证明吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊。这信赖的证明\\n通过王族的“龙之血”代代相传。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "真有意思……\\n尽管力量相似，\\n但起源却不同。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我也能问问\\n与十二龙氏的魂契相关的问题吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "嗯，当然了。\\n任何问题都可以。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "变成龙……摩利支天的样子时\\n是什么感觉？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "因为……性格和语气\\n都和平时的家康完全不同……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "呵呵，刚看到的时候\\n吓到你了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "怎么说好呢……说我自己的身体和灵魂\\n都完全变成了摩利支天，\\n应该会比较好理解吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "一旦释放魂契之力，\\n在那里的就不再是家康，\\n而完全是摩利支天了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "所以看上去像变了一个人\\n也是理所当然的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "自己变成了完全不同的存在……\\n想象不出来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "因为起源与龙化不同，\\n您会这么想也很正常。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "起源……家康，\\n能再问你一个问题吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "魂契……为什么\\n需要十二龙氏缩短寿命？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是龙要求你们献出灵魂的吗？\\n这作为代价是不是太沉重了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "您相当信任龙呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "因为您脸上写着\\n“不希望是这样”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦？\\n不，并、并没有……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "请放心。我们之所以献出灵魂\\n是出于将军世家的信念。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "信念？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "虽然当今日出之国\\n是太平盛世……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "但听闻过去曾是\\n战争不断的乱世。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "为终结那样的时代，\\n初代将军向日出之国的\\n诸龙之长·天照求助。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "因为天照拥有极其强大的力量，\\n所以一直不曾干涉人类。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那位天照之所以行动是因为……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "如您所料，\\n是因为献出灵魂的信念。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "作为“定要创造太平盛世”的信念之证，\\n初代将军献出灵魂，\\n与天照缔结了魂契。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "初代将军贯彻了他的信念，\\n与天照共同平定战乱……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "此后，其子孙便背负着\\n维持太平盛世的使命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "原来如此……\\n日出之国还有这样的历史……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "魂契的代价是沉重的。\\n但那并非是单纯的代价。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "它代表着赌上性命\\n维持日出之国的和平这一信念。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你不会不甘短命吗？\\n不会怨恨命运吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "我是武士。而有勇气贯彻自身信念的人\\n才是真正的武士。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "如果是为了这个信念，\\n就算让我献出生命也在所不惜。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "家康你真强大……\\n居然能平静地接受自己的命运……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "您在我眼中\\n也足够强大了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "您也有\\n拼上性命也要守护的东西吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "有……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我爱的国家、民众、伙伴……\\n还有妹妹，我都想守护。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不，我一定要守护。\\n一定要！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "我的信念和\\n您的强烈愿望是一样的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "区别只在于\\n有没有明确的形式。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "根据我的判断，\\n您也经常不顾危险胡来吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔……确实，\\n伙伴们经常会生我的气。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "您看，一样吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊。还有，我很抱歉。\\n我把魂契往坏处想了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "不会。这恰好证明您很珍惜生命，\\n请不用放在心上。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "主君珍惜生命的国家，\\n才能孕育更多的生命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "今后也请\\n不要忘记这份心境。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110313_01_02_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}